title: Weekly Club Service by ACSES, WCE, Sangli
name: Weekly Club Service by ACSES
body:
ACSES organizes weekly club services on various technical and non-technical topics. According to the students' feedback, the ACSES Main Board members coordinate with the ACSES Club Service Directors and decide the next club service's programs.
  • I with my friend, Anish Joshi, conducted a club service on Trees and Graphs.
  • I encouraged the students to come up on the stage for the game of Marketing Strategy.
  • My senior and friend, Piyush Chaudhari, conducted a session on Stacks and Queues.
  • My seniors and friends, Shivani Sharma, Omkar Puranik, and Mayur Kumbhar conducted a non-technical session on Personality Development.
  • My seniors and friends, Sujata Regoti and Swapnil Walke conducted a session on Competitive Programming.
